# Matflow Design System

This rule defines the **single source of truth** for all UI styling in the Matflow project. Every component, page, and style must follow these guidelines. The design reference is `style.jsonc` at the project root.

---

## Color Palette (Tailwind token → hex)

| Token              | Tailwind class prefix  | Hex       | Usage                                        |
|--------------------|------------------------|-----------|----------------------------------------------|
| `primary`          | `primary`              | `#0D9488` | Main accents, primary buttons, links, icons  |
| `primary-dark`     | `primary-dark`         | `#0F766E` | Hover/active states for primary elements     |
| `primary-light`    | `primary-light`        | `#5EEAD4` | Subtle fills, light accents, focus rings     |
| `accent`           | `accent`               | `#10B981` | Success states, illustration highlights      |
| `text-primary`     | `text` (default)       | `#111827` | Main headings, body text (gray-900)          |
| `text-secondary`   | N/A                    | `#4B5563` | Subtitles, descriptions (gray-600)           |
| `text-light`       | N/A                    | `#6B7280` | Metadata, small text (gray-500)              |
| `background`       | `bg`                   | `#F9FAFB` | Page background (gray-50)                    |
| `surface`          | N/A                    | `#FFFFFF` | Cards, panels, hero sections                 |
| `border`           | N/A                    | `#E5E7EB` | Borders, dividers (gray-200)                 |
| `illustration-bg`  | `illustration-bg`      | `#ECFEF6` | Pale mint containers for illustrations       |
| `success`          | `accent`               | `#10B981` | Positive states                              |
| `warning`          | N/A                    | `#F59E0B` | Warning states                               |
| `error`            | `danger`               | `#EF4444` | Error/destructive states                     |

### Color rules
- **Primary color is TEAL `#0D9488`**, NOT blue. Never use `#3b82f6` as primary.
- Use `bg-primary` / `text-primary` / `border-primary` for teal accents.
- Use `hover:bg-primary-dark` for hover states on primary elements.
- Use `bg-primary/10` for subtle teal backgrounds (icon containers, highlights).
- Backgrounds: `bg-gray-50` (`#F9FAFB`) for page, `bg-white` for cards/surfaces.
- Text: `text-gray-900` for headings, `text-gray-600` for body, `text-gray-500` for metadata.

---

## Typography

### Font family
- **Primary font: Inter** — `font-sans` (configured in Tailwind as the default sans-serif)
- Mono: `font-mono` (system monospace stack)
- **Do NOT use** `font-titillium` or `font-roboto` — these are legacy.

### Font sizes & weights
| Element          | Size               | Weight        | Tailwind classes                    |
|------------------|--------------------|--------------|------------------------------------|
| Brand title (h1) | 3.5rem (56px)      | 700 (bold)   | `text-6xl font-bold uppercase`     |
| Section title    | 2.5rem (40px)      | 700          | `text-4xl font-bold`               |
| Subtitle (h3)    | 1.875rem (30px)    | 600          | `text-3xl font-semibold`           |
| Body text        | 1.125rem (18px)    | 400          | `text-lg font-normal leading-relaxed` |
| Small/labels     | 0.875rem (14px)    | 500          | `text-sm font-medium`              |

### Typography rules
- Brand title (`MATFLOW`) is **uppercase**: use `uppercase tracking-tight`.
- Headings use `tracking-tight` (letter-spacing: -0.025em).
- Body text uses default letter-spacing.
- Buttons do NOT use text-transform.

