## Component Patterns

### Buttons

**Primary button:**
```
bg-primary hover:bg-primary-dark text-white rounded-lg px-6 py-3 font-semibold
shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-200
```

**Secondary button:**
```
bg-transparent border border-gray-300 text-gray-700 rounded-lg px-6 py-3 font-medium
hover:bg-gray-50 transition-all duration-200
```

**Outline button:**
```
Same as secondary — transparent bg with border.
```

### Cards
```
bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6
shadow-soft hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200 hover:-translate-y-0.5
```
- Border radius: `rounded-xl` (12px)
- Padding: `p-6` (24px)
- Shadow: subtle (`shadow-soft` or `shadow-sm`)
- Hover: slight lift + shadow increase

### Hero Section
- Layout: `flex` row on desktop (text left, illustration right)
- Background: `bg-gray-50` or `bg-white` — clean, minimal
- Illustration container: `bg-illustration-bg rounded-2xl` with macOS-style frame
- NO heavy animated gradient orbs — keep it clean and professional
- Subtle parallax or gentle animations only

### Navbar
- `bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-gray-200`
- Brand name: teal colored or use `text-gray-900 font-bold`
- Nav links: `text-gray-700 hover:text-primary` with teal underline on hover
- Login/CTA button: primary button style (teal)
- Badges (Signed In, Admin): `text-sm font-medium` with teal/accent colors
- NO animated gradient orbs in navbar — keep it clean

